。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"一种基于P2P理念的新型网络拓扑结构。"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"KAD 网络","shrink":true},"8":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"741A9","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"53R45","text":"KMP 算法"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"字符串匹配"},"9":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"I7ITG","children":{"0":{"objectClass":"MindNode","ID":"5B2C1","text":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nOtOYVaAhJj8jd5a7CEdaQ"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"二维码"},"objectClass":"NSArray"},"text":"算法与数据结构","remark":"记录编程世界里常用的算法和数据结构。","remarkDisplay":true},"ID":"OKU87","style":100}